&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New customers are coming in through channels you built or fixed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CAC is moving in the right direction and you know why&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ve built things that are working well enough to double down on, and killed some others that aren’t&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We have clearer answers to &quot;where should we be spending?&quot; because of experiments you ran&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Something you shipped is converting measurable better than what existed before.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
