&lt;p&gt;This role is based in Vancouver. We currently work in-office two days per week on Mondays &amp;amp; Thursdays.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Compensation is $150,000–$190,000 CAD base plus equity, for Vancouver-based candidates, depending on seniority. Actual salary takes experience, location, and other factors into account.&lt;/p&gt;
